              },
              "free_text": [
                " The 6He beam used in this experiment was",
                " produced via the 7Li(p,2p)6He reaction using LiF",
                " powder target contained in a graphite holder.",
                "The post-accelerated secondary 6He beam of 27 MeV",
                " energy and intensity of 3 x 106 ions/s."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "197Au target, which was in fact the backing of a",
                " 7LiF target. The thickness of the 197Au layer was",
                " approximately 300 mu-g/cm2. The thickness of the",
                " 7LiF layer was 400 mu-g/cm2."
              ]
            }
          ],
